{"tid":2180566,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全球財務長調查：75％看好拜登贏得大選","createTime":"2020-08-30T03:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T06:36:16.000Z","uid":278587,"like":18,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"a10ace2d1871ca99692a6585aff3edcd4bff4442","tid":2180566,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:12:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/trump-3.jpeg?resize=570%2C380\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.aljazeera.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2Ftrump-3.jpeg%3Fresize%3D570%252C380&h=2d7b3681&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然美國總統川普最近在六個關鍵搖擺州的支持率有上升跡象，不過企業界仍押注拜登（Joe Biden）將在今年大選勝出！根據CNBC發布的全球財務長理事會第三季調查結果顯示，高達四分之三受訪者相信拜登將能擊敗川普，贏得2020年總統大選。<br />\n<br />\nCNBC全球財務長理事會代表的是全球部分大型上市與私人企業，這些企業涵蓋各行各業，其管理市值加總起來共超過5兆美元。調查時間為8月7日到22日。<br />\n<br />\n調查發現，75％財務長看好民主黨總統候選人拜登將在今年大選脫穎而出。另外20％認為川普將再度當選，還有5％表示不確定或沒有表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n除了總統選舉，在國會改選方面，63％北美財務長不認為參議院或眾議院的選舉結果會出現翻盤，25％相信民主黨將重新奪回參議院主導權、6％預期共和黨將執掌眾議院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200829003531-260410?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20200829003531-260410%3Fchdtv&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLGCkd6W2E%2BSZ990UparCCSw%3D&h=11aad048\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200829003531-260410?chdtv</a>"},{"pid":"d837fc7f614d79dd80b69eef0e5ba685a3561ee7","tid":2180566,"uid":257191,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:15:05.000Z","msg":"我登必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575372506db17738198940c4140a02b5d7dbcc68","tid":2180566,"uid":10201,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:15:41.000Z","msg":"拜登必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073d6b0c17904b9861a7f1f16ad4e7c1f342fb10","tid":2180566,"uid":196222,"l